Package: imbCalib
Type: Package
Title: Probability Calibration for Imbalanced Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yu Yang
Maintainer: Yu Yang <yang6367@umn.edu>
Description: This package intends to calibrate probabilities for imbalanced data, using 
    bagged undersampling method. It also provides functionality to calculate both standard
    Brier score and stratified Brier score. Besides, calibration curves and comparison plot 
    could be otained by using two plotting functions inside the package.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
